### Create a new order for a client (multi-products)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/commandes/clients/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "articles": [
    { "produitId": 3, "quantite": 2 },
    { "produitId": 2, "quantite": 1 }
  ],
  "codePromo": "PROMO-AB12"
}

### Create a new order WITHOUT promo code (no promo discount applied)
# When you omit codePromo, the promo discount is not applied.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/commandes/clients/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "articles": [
    { "produitId": 3, "quantite": 2 },
    { "produitId": 2, "quantite": 1 }
  ]
}

### Get order by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/commandes/1

### Search orders (pagination + filters)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/commandes?start=0&size=10&clientId=1&statut=PENDING&totalMin=100&totalMax=10000

### Confirm order (requires montantRestant = 0)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/commandes/1/confirm

### Cancel order (only if PENDING)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/commandes/1/cancel
